data.description: Discover the potential in this charming rambler tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac, offering the perfect opportunity to create your dream home. With your finishing touches, this residence can be transformed into a cozy haven you'll love coming back to. The carport provides convenient covered parking, protecting your vehicle from the elements. Step inside to reveal the timeless beauty of wood flooring that adds character and warmth to the living spaces. The open floor plan beckons for your creative touches to maximize its potential. Picture evenings by the fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance during colder months. A major highlight of this property is the walkout basement, offering endless possibilities for expansion, a family room, or an additional bedroom. It's an excellent canvas to tailor the space to your unique vision. This home is ready for a makeover and represents a fantastic investment opportunity in a sought-after location. Bring your renovation ideas and make this home the gem it's destined to become. Don't miss out on the chance to create a space that reflects your style and preferences.
